scene_description: A cartoon-style black crow is depicted flying across a bright blue sky with sparse clouds, above a green, hilly landscape.
A crow is dropping a rock into a pot of water, attempting to raise the water level.
A crow stands on a rock, dropping pebbles into a pitcher to raise the water level and drink.
A crow is dropping stones into a pitcher containing water, attempting to raise the water level.
A clever crow drops pebbles into a pitcher of water to raise the water level so it can drink.
